  "name": "Aspose.BarCode for .NET Examples Agent",
  "description": "Provides 1124 build-validated, standalone C# code examples for barcode generation and recognition using Aspose.BarCode for .NET. Covers 1D, 2D, postal, and special barcode types across 21 categories.",
  "capabilities": [
    "Generate C# examples for 1D barcodes (Code128, Code39, EAN, UPC, ITF, Codabar, and 50+ symbologies)",
    "Generate C# examples for 2D barcodes (QR Code, DataMatrix, PDF417, Aztec, MaxiCode, GS1 DataBar)",
    "Generate C# examples for postal barcodes (Mailmark 4-state and 2D, USPS, Australia Post)",
    "Generate C# examples for special barcodes (HIBC LIC, Swiss QR Code, PatchCode)",
    "Generate C# examples for barcode recognition and reading from images, PDFs, and streams",
    "Generate C# examples for PDF integration (image embed and interactive ButtonField)",
    "Generate C# examples for image customization (colors, resolution, padding, rotation, X-dimension)",
    "Generate C# examples for batch processing and XML configuration export/import"
  ],
  "input_formats": [
    "natural language task description"
  ],
  "output_formats": [
    "C# source file (.cs)",
